flowchart LR
    Client([Client])
    Hasher[Hash Function<br/>MurmurHash3]
    Lookup[Ring Lookup<br/>walk clockwise]
    Ring[(Hash Ring<br/>sorted vnode positions)]
    VNodeMap[(vnode to server<br/>mapping)]
    Server[Owning Server<br/>S1 / S2 / S3]
    Gossip[Gossip Membership<br/>epoch + heartbeat]

    Client -->|key K| Hasher
    Hasher -->|hash position| Lookup
    Lookup -->|first vnode >= hash| Ring
    Lookup -->|resolve owner| VNodeMap
    VNodeMap -->|route| Server
    Gossip -.->|membership updates| Ring
    Gossip -.->|membership updates| VNodeMap

    classDef external fill:#1e2533,stroke:#3a4a6e,color:#cfd6e6
    classDef service fill:#1a3a2e,stroke:#3a6e54,color:#cfe6d6
    classDef store fill:#1e2a3e,stroke:#3a5a8e,color:#cfdcef
    classDef config fill:#3a2e1a,stroke:#6e5a3a,color:#efdfcf

    class Client external
    class Hasher,Lookup,Server service
    class Ring,VNodeMap store
    class Gossip config
